      "commentBody": "<span class=\"comment\"><font color=\"#000000\">DuckDuckGo (Paoli, PA, USA) - LOCAL OR REMOTE.<p>We would welcome 1-2 additions to our small core search engineering team.  This team works across our full architecture (<a href=\"https://dukgo.com/help/en_US/company/architecture\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://dukgo.com/help/en_US/company/architecture</a>) though does more back-end and data algo than front-end and dev-ops, which are primarily handled elsewhere.</p><p>Previous search experience or extensive experience with our particular architecture is not necessary, though this is not a junior level position.</p></font><p><font color=\"#000000\"><a href=\"https://dukgo.com/help/en_US/company/hiring\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://dukgo.com/help/en_US/company/hiring</a></font></p><p><font size=\"1\"><u><a href=\"reply?id=6310351&amp;whence=%69%74%65%6d%3f%69%64%3d%36%33%31%30%32%33%34\">reply</a></u></font></p></span>",
