      "commentBody": "<span class=\"comment\"><font color=\"#000000\">Chartbeat - New York, NY - Frontend or Backend or Infrastructure Engineer, Data Scientist, UX Designer (full time)<p><a href=\"https://chartbeat.com/jobs/\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://chartbeat.com/jobs/</a></p><p>Chartbeat is a real-time analytics service designed for real-time action used by everyone from The Wall Street Journal to Al Jazeera. We're democratizing data by putting it in the hands of people who need it to make decisions and take action - right now. Just before our 4th birthday we moved into our own sprawling office in Union Square, Manhattan. We are packing it full of incredible talent. Thanks to years of hard work and amazing funding by some of the top investors in the world (Draper Fisher Jurvetson, Index Ventures, and Betaworks) we're growing, and growing quickly.</p></font><p><font color=\"#000000\">jobs[AT]chartbeat.com</font></p><p><font size=\"1\"><u><a href=\"reply?id=6310520&amp;whence=%69%74%65%6d%3f%69%64%3d%36%33%31%30%32%33%34\">reply</a></u></font></p></span>",
