      "commentBody": "<span class=\"comment\"><font color=\"#000000\">EasyPost - San Francisco (REMOTE -- but willing to move to bay area)<p>We're quickly growing our team and looking for early hires. We recently received top 8 at Demo Day, have a host of new investors and funding, and are ready to get back to building.</p><p>We're down to Earth, active, and have a great time working on a product with real revenue and that customers love.</p><p>We're looking for senior developers who want to get in early, take over an area of the API, and make it great.</p></font><p><font color=\"#000000\">Interested? Email us at work@easypost dot com with what you'd like to add/change about our API. If we're a fit for you, we'll let you build it!</font></p><p><font size=\"1\"><u><a href=\"reply?id=6310752&amp;whence=%69%74%65%6d%3f%69%64%3d%36%33%31%30%32%33%34\">reply</a></u></font></p></span>",
