      "commentBody": "<span class=\"comment\"><font color=\"#000000\">Want to work on Ubuntu? Canonical is hiring.<p>General careers page : <a href=\"http://www.canonical.com/about-canonical/careers\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://www.canonical.com/about-canonical/careers</a></p><p>Specific to my team, I'm looking for someone to keep up with X.org, Mir and the various graphics related packages: \n<a href=\"https://ch.tbe.taleo.net/CH03/ats/careers/requisition.jsp?org=CANONICAL&amp;cws=1&amp;rid=652\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://ch.tbe.taleo.net/CH03/ats/careers/requisition.jsp?or...</a></p></font><p><font color=\"#000000\">EDIT: I should note, nearly all positions are remote including the one on my team.</font></p><p><font size=\"1\"><u><a href=\"reply?id=6310824&amp;whence=%69%74%65%6d%3f%69%64%3d%36%33%31%30%32%33%34\">reply</a></u></font></p></span>",
