      "commentBody": "<span class=\"comment\"><font color=\"#000000\">MapBox - San Francisco and Washington DC<p>MapBox is looking for developers and designers, an Operations Manager, and a Business Development Lead.</p><p><a href=\"http://www.mapbox.com/jobs/\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://www.mapbox.com/jobs/</a></p><p>We're a team of 30 or so artists, developers, designers and strategists working on an open platform for maps. Our platform powers everything from apps like Foursquare, GitHub and Evernote to news stories on NPR and USAToday to simple maps on personal blogs and wedding websites. Much of our work is powered by open source and open data and we're often in touch with folks at OpenStreetMap, the US Census Bureau, USGS, and NASA.</p><p>Check out what we have been working on lately on our blog:</p></font><p><font color=\"#000000\"><a href=\"http://www.mapbox.com/blog/\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://www.mapbox.com/blog/</a></font></p><p><font size=\"1\"><u><a href=\"reply?id=6311480&amp;whence=%69%74%65%6d%3f%69%64%3d%36%33%31%30%32%33%34\">reply</a></u></font></p></span>",
